.\" %W% %G%
.TH Glayer.info 2G G-language
.SH NAME
Glayer.info \- Retrieves layer information for cell files
.br
.I (G Language Tool)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBGlayer.info\fR [\fIlayer_name\fR]
.br
\fBGlayer.info\fR [layer\*=\fIlayer_name\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Glayer.info 
results in the production of a table listing various information about 
a user-chosen map layer.
.pp
Following is the result of 
